+## Reflect Prompt Integration
+
+### Location
+`crates/myosu-tui/src/pipe.rs` вҖ” extend `PipeMode`
+
+### Flow
+
+```
+1. Hand completes
+2. PipeMode outputs HAND COMPLETE block
+3. PipeMode outputs "reflect> " prompt to stdout
+4. PipeMode reads line from stdin
+5. If line is empty вҶ’ skip, continue
+6. If line is non-empty вҶ’ append to JournalEntry.reflection
+7. Continue to next hand
+```
+
+### Output Format
+
+```
+HAND COMPLETE
+result: +14bb (showdown, Aвҷ  KвҷҘ vs QвҷЈ JвҷЈ)
+session: +28bb over 47 hands
+
+reflect>
+```
+
