+## Lobby Integration (Pipe Mode Without --subnet)
+
+### Location
+`crates/myosu-tui/src/pipe.rs` вҖ” extend `PipeMode`
+
+### Flow
+
+```
+1. myosu-play --pipe (no --subnet)
+2. PipeMode outputs MYOSU/LOBBY
+3. Agent types "info <id>" or "<id>"
